rows.label: tlk70000019_03_msg0001
rows.name:
Laura-sama, I was surprised to hear
that you'd been knighted!

rows.label: tlk70000019_03_msg0002
rows.name:
Then again, if anyone deserved to be
knighted it was you. You risked your
life to protect us from the Grail.

rows.label: tlk70000019_03_msg0003
rows.name:
I think this country would be a better
place if there were more women like
you around.

rows.label: tlk70000019_03_msg0004
rows.name:
These days men can't be relied on to
do diddly-squat.

rows.label: tlk70000019_03_msg0005
rows.name:
You're ten times as strong as my
husband. No, make that a hundred
times as strong!

rows.label: tlk70000019_03_msg0006
rows.name: Ahaha, listen to me rambling on!
